@@ -0,0 +1,6 @@
+# Node's bundled OpenSSL source omits documentation inputs after generating its
+# checked-in build metadata, but OpenSSL Configure still loads doc/build.info.
+# There are no documentation targets in the AgentOS static-library build.
+# Node's vendoring process is documented here:
+# https://github.com/nodejs/node/blob/v24.15.0/doc/contributing/maintaining/maintaining-openssl.md
+# OpenSSL build.info syntax: https://github.com/openssl/openssl/blob/openssl-3.5.5/Configurations/README.md
